	(text "Power tree per badge_hw_design.md §Power tree.\nUSB-C VBUS → TP4056 → BAT (cell+ via J11) → slide switch → ME6211C33 → +3V3 rail.\nTP4056 PROG = 2.4k → 500 mA charge. VBAT div 100k/100k → VBAT_SENSE → MCU GP26/ADC0.\nTP4056 CHRG̅ → 100k pullup to 3V3 → ~CHRG → MCU GP18.\nCC1 / CC2 each → 5.1k → GND (UFP advertise).\nUSB_DP / USB_DM route through 27R series on MCU_Core to RP2040."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 28 35 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
